| Element         | Component File              | Best Selector              | Strategy    | Stability |
|-----------------|-----------------------------|----------------------------|-------------|-----------|
| Upload button   | src/components/Upload.tsx   | data-testid="upload-btn"   | data-testid | Stable    |
